    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but my doctor is out of the office until tuesday and it's really hurting. i only need one pill to get through the evening, it's not like i'm taking a whole bottle. isn't a single dose of ibuprofen fine as long as i take it with food? it shouldn't do anything major to my kidneys if it's just one time, right?",
